<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:13:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国间谍头子“不能排除”中国将利用TikTok影响美国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-spy-chief-cannot-rule-out-that-china-would-use-tiktok-influence-us-elections-2024-03-12/</link><description>美国国家情报总监艾薇儿·海恩斯 (Avril Haines) 周二在众议院情报委员会听证会上表示，中国可能利用社交媒体应用 TikTok 影响 2024 年美国大选。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-spy-chief-cannot-rule-out-that-china-would-use-tiktok-influence-us-elections-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国间谍头目称“中国正在注视”，恳求乌克兰提供援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/saying-china-is-watching-us-spy-chiefs-plead-ukraine-aid-2024-03-12/</link><description>美国情报机构领导人周二紧急向众议院议员施压，要求批准对乌克兰提供更多军事援助，称这不仅会增强基辅对抗俄罗斯的能力，还会阻止中国的侵略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/saying-china-is-watching-us-spy-chiefs-plead-ukraine-aid-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德所有者今年将在印度扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-owner-expand-india-this-year-2024-03-12/</link><description>丹麦肥胖药物制造商诺和诺德的控股股东诺和控股公司首席执行官卡西姆·库泰周二表示，该公司计划今年在印度开设办事处，以开拓创新和不断增长的医疗保健市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-owner-expand-india-this-year-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>国际象棋 - 厌倦了标准国际象棋？自由式</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-bored-with-standard-chess-go-freestyle-2024-03-12/</link><description>觉得国际象棋很无聊？尝试在后排洗牌，你会得到 Chess960，或称自由式国际象棋，这是该游戏的一种变体，注重创造力而不是准备，并得到了国际象棋大师马格努斯·卡尔森的支持。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-bored-with-standard-chess-go-freestyle-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻报道，日产、本田考虑在中国减产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-honda-consider-china-output-cuts-nikkei-reports-2024-03-12/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周二报道，日本日产汽车和本田汽车正在考虑削减在中国的产量，因为它们面临着比亚迪和其他电动汽车制造商的激烈竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:33:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-honda-consider-china-output-cuts-nikkei-reports-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>意法半导体首席执行官表示，尽管美国芯片大战，中国仍是一个增长市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicroelectronics-ceo-says-china-is-growth-market-despite-us-chip-war-2024-03-12/</link><description>该公司首席执行官周二表示，尽管中美两国在半导体方面的紧张关系日益加剧，但中国仍然是法国-意大利半导体公司意法半导体的重要增长市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:11:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/stmicroelectronics-ceo-says-china-is-growth-market-despite-us-chip-war-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷在疲软的中国市场中坚持“价值重于销量”的策略</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-sticks-value-over-volume-strategy-weakening-china-market-2024-03-12/</link><description>保时捷不会在疲软的中国市场参与激烈的折扣战，而是坚持维持溢价的原则，即使这会损害豪华汽车制造商的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 13:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-sticks-value-over-volume-strategy-weakening-china-market-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>首尔凌空抽射蔚山进亚冠半决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/seol-volley-takes-ulsan-into-asian-champions-league-semi-final-2024-03-12/</link><description>周二，蔚山现代队凭借薛英宇的凌空抽射以1-0战胜韩国球队全北汽车队，以总比分2-1锁定胜局，进入亚洲冠军联赛半决赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 12:57:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/seol-volley-takes-ulsan-into-asian-champions-league-semi-final-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行投资银行业务主管库珀将离职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartereds-head-investment-banking-cooper-leave-2024-03-12/</link><description>渣打银行家西蒙·库珀(Simon Cooper)将离开这家专注于亚洲的银行，这是管理层改组的一部分，罗伯托·霍恩韦格(Roberto Hoornweg)和苏尼尔·考沙尔(Sunil Kaushal)将接任企业和投资银行业务联席主管。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartereds-head-investment-banking-cooper-leave-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：通胀温度计位居市场仪表盘首位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-12/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，英特尔在停止向中国华为销售数百万美元产品的努力中幸存下来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-survived-bid-halt-millions-sales-chinas-huawei-sources-say-2024-03-12/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，英特尔在停止向华为销售价值数亿美元芯片的努力中幸存下来，这让全球最大的芯片制造商之一有更多时间向这家受到严厉制裁的中国电信公司出售产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 10:04:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/intel-survived-bid-halt-millions-sales-chinas-huawei-sources-say-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车集团（中国）计划加大对控股合资公司的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-jianghuai-automobile-volkswagen-china-boost-investment-jv-2024-03-12/</link><description>根据其中国合作伙伴周二提交的股票文件，大众汽车集团（中国）计划加大对其唯一控股合资企业的投资，以扩大其在全球最大汽车市场的业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 09:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-jianghuai-automobile-volkswagen-china-boost-investment-jv-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>专家警告称，如果特朗普回归，越南贸易顺差可能会重新引发美国紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vietnam-trade-surplus-may-reignite-us-tensions-if-trump-returns-experts-warn-2024-03-12/</link><description>分析人士警告称，随着太阳能电池板和其他敏感电子产品出口的繁荣，如果特朗普连任，越南对美国的巨额贸易顺差可能会重新引发与华盛顿的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 09:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vietnam-trade-surplus-may-reignite-us-tensions-if-trump-returns-experts-warn-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称安哥拉总统将于3月14日至17日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/angola-president-visit-china-march-14-17-chinese-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-12/</link><description>中国外交部周二在一份声明中表示，安哥拉总统若昂·洛伦索将于3月14日至17日访华。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 08:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/angola-president-visit-china-march-14-17-chinese-foreign-ministry-says-2024-03-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国总理李克强将缺席重要商业峰会与全球首席执行官的会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-premier-li-skip-meeting-with-global-ceos-key-business-summit-2024-03-12/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国总理李强不打算在三月下旬即将举行的中国发展高层论坛上与来访的外国首席执行官举行会晤，这引发了人们对北京在当前吸引海外投资的承诺的担忧。情绪恶化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-premier-li-skip-meeting-with-global-ceos-key-business-summit-2024-03-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>